lead_paragraph: England soccer coach Roy Hodgson's four-year reign came to an abrupt end after their shock 2-1 defeat by tiny Iceland at the Euro 2016 round of 16 stage on Monday.

headline.print_headline: England Manager Hodgson Resigns After Euro 2016 Exit
headline.main: England Manager Hodgson Resigns After Euro 2016 Exit
